# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
#
# The SPA fallback (/* /index.html 200) is NOT included here.
# With prerendering, every route has its own dist/route/index.html.
# CF Pages serves each route directly -- no rewrite rule needed.
#
# Including the SPA fallback causes an infinite redirect loop:
# CF's Pretty URLs feature rewrites /about/ to dist/about/index.html,
# which triggers the /* rule, which rewrites to /index.html, which
# CF redirects back to /about/... and so on.
#
# If you ever revert to SPA-only mode (no prerendering), restore:
#   /* /index.html 200
#
# Add app-specific redirects below as needed:
# /old-path    /new-path    301
